WEBVTT

00:00:02.320 --> 00:00:04.160
To avoid a repeat of the Ma Shan Bao incident,

00:00:04.400 --> 00:00:06.200
solitary confinement and news blackout...

00:00:06.480 --> 00:00:07.599
are necessary measures...

00:00:07.600 --> 00:00:09.080
to ensure Qin Yi Wei's safety.

00:00:09.280 --> 00:00:11.680
This approach will only keep things hidden for a short while.

00:00:12.240 --> 00:00:14.199
Once this case goes to court,

00:00:14.200 --> 00:00:15.200
it will be exposed.

00:00:15.680 --> 00:00:16.720
Then,

00:00:17.360 --> 00:00:18.879
Han Kui Long will find out...

00:00:18.880 --> 00:00:20.319
that the one who almost killed his son...

00:00:20.320 --> 00:00:21.480
is Qin Yi Wei.

00:00:23.400 --> 00:00:24.640
I suggest that from now on,

00:00:24.880 --> 00:00:26.080
everyone cancels their leave.

00:00:26.160 --> 00:00:27.160
For 24 hours,

00:00:27.161 --> 00:00:28.279
make sure someone keeps an eye on Han Lie...

00:00:28.280 --> 00:00:29.280
and Qi Chang Rong.

00:00:29.320 --> 00:00:30.760
Why keep an eye on Qi Chang Rong?

00:00:31.280 --> 00:00:32.280
People like Qi Chang Rong...

00:00:32.440 --> 00:00:33.840
love to fish in troubled waters.

00:00:33.960 --> 00:00:35.240
He only wants chaos.

00:00:47.360 --> 00:00:49.040
Judge Qin, you can talk in private.

00:00:49.480 --> 00:00:50.480
Call me when you're done.

00:00:50.720 --> 00:00:51.720
Okay, thank you.

00:00:55.640 --> 00:00:56.640
Yi Wei.

00:00:57.920 --> 00:00:58.960
Are you alright?

00:01:02.040 --> 00:01:03.040
Not really.

00:01:04.840 --> 00:01:05.840
But I'm hanging in there.

00:01:07.800 --> 00:01:08.800
Dad.

00:01:09.640 --> 00:01:11.080
Don't fight with Grandma anymore.

00:01:12.320 --> 00:01:13.440
She's also very upset...

00:01:14.720 --> 00:01:15.920
that I ended up like this.

00:01:26.000 --> 00:01:27.000
Grandma gave it to me.

00:01:27.920 --> 00:01:28.920
I couldn't find it.

00:01:29.280 --> 00:01:30.360
So it was with you.

00:01:36.640 --> 00:01:37.680
Yi Wei.

00:01:38.440 --> 00:01:39.440
Don't be afraid.

00:01:40.280 --> 00:01:41.520
First, this is your first offense.

00:01:42.400 --> 00:01:43.560
You turned yourself in.

00:01:44.320 --> 00:01:45.560
Besides, it was an accident.

00:01:46.640 --> 00:01:48.320
The judge won't give you a heavy sentence.

00:01:49.120 --> 00:01:50.200
Dad.

00:01:54.000 --> 00:01:55.560
It wasn't an accident.

00:01:57.840 --> 00:01:58.840
What did you say?

00:02:03.120 --> 00:02:05.320
I intentionally hit that scumbag.

00:02:09.360 --> 00:02:10.360
Intentionally?

00:02:10.640 --> 00:02:11.920
I did it for my mom.

00:02:14.480 --> 00:02:15.480
Mom?

00:02:16.600 --> 00:02:19.120
I knew why Mom killed herself.

00:03:49.000 --> 00:03:53.000
(Justice Is Mine)

00:03:53.040 --> 00:03:56.000
(Episode 12)

00:04:00.560 --> 00:04:01.560
Dad.

00:04:03.200 --> 00:04:04.919
Back then, you were either in court...

00:04:04.920 --> 00:04:06.000
or in meetings every day.

00:04:07.280 --> 00:04:09.160
You never had time to be at home.

00:04:10.880 --> 00:04:12.280
But Mom said it was okay.

00:04:13.800 --> 00:04:15.520
Because she knew what your dream was.

00:04:18.280 --> 00:04:20.240
Just because you sentenced Han Kui Long to prison,

00:04:22.200 --> 00:04:24.240
that scumbag raped Mom!

00:04:24.560 --> 00:04:25.560
Don't be nervous!

00:04:26.560 --> 00:04:28.040
It's okay.

00:04:30.080 --> 00:04:31.080
It's okay.

00:04:32.640 --> 00:04:34.360
Scream louder!

00:04:42.360 --> 00:04:43.360
Look at me.

00:04:44.160 --> 00:04:45.240
My name is Han Gang.

00:04:46.160 --> 00:04:47.880
My dad's name is Han Kui Long.

00:04:48.480 --> 00:04:49.480
Remember that.

00:04:50.360 --> 00:04:51.720
Tell your husband about it.

00:04:58.960 --> 00:04:59.960
Remember me.

00:05:01.520 --> 00:05:03.160
Call me whenever you want to have fun.

00:05:05.240 --> 00:05:06.240
Bye.

00:05:10.160 --> 00:05:11.640
I will never forget...

00:05:12.040 --> 00:05:13.440
that scumbag's face.

00:05:29.520 --> 00:05:30.560
It's okay.

00:05:31.400 --> 00:05:32.400
It's okay.

00:05:32.440 --> 00:05:33.640
I'm okay.

00:05:35.360 --> 00:05:37.040
She didn't want me to call the police.

00:05:37.680 --> 00:05:39.120
She didn't want to affect you.

00:05:40.040 --> 00:05:42.240
So she didn't want anyone to know.

00:05:44.240 --> 00:05:45.240
But the next day,

00:05:45.241 --> 00:05:46.439
she couldn't get over it.

00:05:46.440 --> 00:05:47.600
She killed herself.

00:05:55.680 --> 00:05:56.880
I was so angry.

00:05:58.200 --> 00:05:59.760
I hated myself so much.

00:06:01.800 --> 00:06:03.840
One day, I saw him on the street.

00:06:06.080 --> 00:06:08.200
He was wearing Mom's necklace.

00:06:09.440 --> 00:06:11.240
I immediately followed him in your car.

00:06:14.200 --> 00:06:15.720
I wanted him dead!

00:06:17.000 --> 00:06:18.360
I want revenge!

00:07:02.560 --> 00:07:04.200
(Beloved Wife)

00:07:38.440 --> 00:07:39.440
Honey.

00:07:40.400 --> 00:07:41.800
You tie my tie for me every day.

00:07:42.320 --> 00:07:43.439
I feel like it's my...

00:07:43.440 --> 00:07:44.720
most glorious moment.

00:07:51.240 --> 00:07:52.680
You really can't turn it down this time?

00:07:54.640 --> 00:07:56.720
The presiding judge suddenly fell ill.

00:07:56.920 --> 00:07:58.040
If I don't take over,

00:07:58.240 --> 00:07:59.320
the case will be postponed.

00:07:59.720 --> 00:08:00.720
Then the defense...

00:08:00.720 --> 00:08:01.720
will have further objections.

00:08:01.920 --> 00:08:02.920
I can't turn it down.

00:08:04.280 --> 00:08:05.840
But the gang of Han's...

00:08:06.120 --> 00:08:07.520
has a lot of clout.

00:08:08.560 --> 00:08:09.880
I know what you're worried about.

00:08:10.360 --> 00:08:11.880
I can't back down because I'm scared.

00:08:12.840 --> 00:08:14.080
I also have to tell everyone...

00:08:14.600 --> 00:08:16.760
that nothing is above the law.

00:08:22.720 --> 00:08:23.720
How's it? Is it done?

00:08:31.360 --> 00:08:32.640
Dad, catch!

00:08:35.360 --> 00:08:36.360
It's my turn now.

00:08:40.640 --> 00:08:41.720
Dinner's ready.

00:08:42.120 --> 00:08:43.120
Honey.

00:08:44.040 --> 00:08:45.040
Sit down.

00:08:45.080 --> 00:08:46.080
Dad,

00:08:46.081 --> 00:08:47.440
next week when we go to the game,

00:08:48.120 --> 00:08:49.200
we'll both wear blue.

00:08:49.600 --> 00:08:51.640
Mum will wear red.

00:08:52.680 --> 00:08:53.680
Wei Wei,

00:08:53.681 --> 00:08:54.879
do you know that your dad...

00:08:54.880 --> 00:08:56.720
is presiding over a very important case?

00:08:57.160 --> 00:08:58.160
Here we go again.

00:08:59.120 --> 00:09:00.880
When will Dad stop presiding over cases?

00:09:01.320 --> 00:09:02.320
It's like this.

00:09:02.321 --> 00:09:04.240
Because this case is quite complicated.

00:09:04.680 --> 00:09:05.840
I'm going to judge a gang leader,

00:09:06.560 --> 00:09:07.839
so it will take a long time.

00:09:07.840 --> 00:09:09.439
The relationships of those involved are complex.

00:09:09.440 --> 00:09:10.679
So this trip of ours will be...

00:09:10.680 --> 00:09:11.680
Dad.

00:09:12.120 --> 00:09:13.160
You're a judge.

00:09:13.520 --> 00:09:14.920
Yet you often break your promises.

00:09:15.680 --> 00:09:17.040
Watching the game was your idea.

00:09:17.720 --> 00:09:18.720
What do you mean?

00:09:18.880 --> 00:09:19.880
Besides court cases,

00:09:20.360 --> 00:09:21.600
neither Mom nor I matter?

00:09:22.920 --> 00:09:24.480
Why don't we wait for them to come next time?

00:09:25.480 --> 00:09:27.359
Or we'll just have to wait until your dad takes off work...

00:09:27.360 --> 00:09:28.360
and we'll go abroad.

00:09:28.361 --> 00:09:29.520
We can fly over to watch the game.

00:09:29.920 --> 00:09:30.920
Go by yourself.

00:09:31.800 --> 00:09:32.840
Wei Wei.

00:09:33.840 --> 00:09:34.840
Ignore him.

00:09:35.280 --> 00:09:36.280
The most important thing is,

00:09:36.400 --> 00:09:37.400
do you also think that way?

00:09:38.600 --> 00:09:39.800
I'm not a kid.

00:09:40.720 --> 00:09:42.320
Don't worry. I'll just coax him, and he'll be fine.

00:09:44.160 --> 00:09:45.999
After I'm done with this case, I'll apply for a long leave.

00:09:46.000 --> 00:09:47.160
We'll go on a family trip.

00:09:47.360 --> 00:09:48.440
Let's have a sweet vacation.

00:09:48.880 --> 00:09:49.880
Sure.

00:09:49.920 --> 00:09:50.920
Let's go camping.

00:09:51.120 --> 00:09:52.120
Wei Wei likes it.

00:09:53.920 --> 00:09:54.920
Let's eat first.

00:10:04.880 --> 00:10:05.880
Honey.

00:10:05.920 --> 00:10:06.960
What's wrong with you, honey?

00:10:07.360 --> 00:10:08.360
Honey.

00:10:09.760 --> 00:10:10.999
Why are you so cold?

00:10:11.000 --> 00:10:12.680
Honey, why are you so cold?

00:10:13.440 --> 00:10:14.440
Why are you so cold?

00:10:14.640 --> 00:10:16.320
What's wrong?

00:10:16.480 --> 00:10:17.480
- What's wrong? - Mom.

00:10:17.481 --> 00:10:18.920
Why are you so cold?

00:10:20.440 --> 00:10:22.360
Yi Wei, bring me the blanket.

00:10:22.520 --> 00:10:23.840
Your mom is cold. Hurry up.

00:10:24.160 --> 00:10:25.160
Hurry up.

00:10:25.280 --> 00:10:26.600
Bring me the blanket!

00:10:27.040 --> 00:10:28.040
Hold her.

00:10:28.080 --> 00:10:29.080
Hold your mom.

00:10:29.680 --> 00:10:30.680
Honey.

00:10:31.920 --> 00:10:33.080
You're so cold. Your mom is so cold.

00:10:33.480 --> 00:10:34.480
Honey.

00:10:35.960 --> 00:10:36.960
Honey.

00:10:37.000 --> 00:10:38.000
No, honey.

00:10:38.001 --> 00:10:39.280
Honey, no. No!

00:10:39.400 --> 00:10:40.400
No, honey!

00:12:55.840 --> 00:12:57.400
The person who hit my brother has been arrested.

00:12:58.480 --> 00:12:59.560
His name is Qin Yi Wei.

00:13:00.000 --> 00:13:01.080
He's the son of a judge.

00:13:01.560 --> 00:13:02.560
However,

00:13:02.800 --> 00:13:04.160
the police have sealed the information.

00:13:04.720 --> 00:13:06.080
We don't know where he is being held.

00:13:06.400 --> 00:13:08.080
The detention room at the Eastern District Police Station.

00:13:11.600 --> 00:13:13.600
Dad, you're in prison, yet you're so well-informed.

00:13:15.600 --> 00:13:16.600
As long as there are people...

00:13:18.040 --> 00:13:19.040
and money,

00:13:19.920 --> 00:13:21.280
what information can't you buy?

00:13:24.600 --> 00:13:25.880
When the court sentences him to prison,

00:13:27.000 --> 00:13:29.200
I guarantee he won't live to see the day he gets out.

00:13:30.280 --> 00:13:31.920
I'm the only one who can judge...

00:13:32.360 --> 00:13:34.240
who harmed my son.

00:13:36.000 --> 00:13:37.480
I want to sentence him to death.

00:13:40.720 --> 00:13:41.720
Okay.

00:13:42.600 --> 00:13:43.600
I'll make the arrangements.

00:13:48.720 --> 00:13:50.360
How is your brother recovering?

00:13:53.360 --> 00:13:54.360
He's doing well.

00:13:56.800 --> 00:13:58.320
Yesterday, he even asked me if I could...

00:13:58.680 --> 00:13:59.960
arrange two girls to serve him.

00:14:03.640 --> 00:14:05.400
I think he'll recover soon.

00:14:10.840 --> 00:14:11.840
Xiao Lie,

00:14:13.240 --> 00:14:14.240
you can do it.

00:14:15.560 --> 00:14:16.600
Our Han family...

00:14:17.640 --> 00:14:19.400
will depend on you two brothers.

00:14:23.200 --> 00:14:24.280
I got it, Dad.

00:14:27.520 --> 00:14:28.520
Get in!

00:14:29.200 --> 00:14:30.200
Squat down.

00:14:30.240 --> 00:14:31.240
Squat down! Don't move!

00:14:31.800 --> 00:14:32.800
I'll leave them to you.

00:14:32.840 --> 00:14:34.120
- They're all hooligans. - Okay.

00:14:34.640 --> 00:14:36.200
Sit properly. What kind of attitude is that?

00:14:36.560 --> 00:14:38.480
Shouldn't you be more polite? Sit properly.

00:14:38.640 --> 00:14:39.640
Who's your boss?

00:14:39.800 --> 00:14:40.800
It's none of your business.

00:14:41.000 --> 00:14:42.000
What's going on here?

00:14:42.160 --> 00:14:43.320
Officer, what are you doing?

00:14:43.440 --> 00:14:44.440
Why did you arrest me?

00:14:44.800 --> 00:14:45.920
You resisted arrest,

00:14:46.240 --> 00:14:47.240
assaulted an officer,

00:14:47.600 --> 00:14:48.919
and possessed an offensive weapon.

00:14:48.920 --> 00:14:49.960
That's why I arrested you, alright?

00:14:50.080 --> 00:14:51.080
Sit tight.

00:14:51.120 --> 00:14:52.400
Or I'll charge you with obstruction of justice.

00:14:53.160 --> 00:14:54.240
Hello. Yes.

00:14:54.360 --> 00:14:55.360
Got it.

00:14:55.400 --> 00:14:56.440
I'll bring it over after taking statements.

00:14:56.680 --> 00:14:57.680
Okay.

00:14:59.080 --> 00:15:00.120
My hand is about to break.

00:15:00.240 --> 00:15:01.599
You never change.

00:15:01.600 --> 00:15:02.679
How dare you steal in the police station?

00:15:02.680 --> 00:15:03.680
Watch out.

00:15:03.681 --> 00:15:04.960
Luckily, he didn't steal your gun.

00:15:05.160 --> 00:15:06.160
Okay, thank you.

00:15:06.440 --> 00:15:07.440
Officer Hu.

00:15:07.840 --> 00:15:09.199
Do you know how chaotic it is out there?

00:15:09.200 --> 00:15:10.360
It's all premeditated.

00:15:10.760 --> 00:15:12.560
Someone is indeed declaring war on us.

00:15:13.080 --> 00:15:14.880
Their target is Qin Yi Wei.

00:15:15.040 --> 00:15:17.080
All the suspects we just arrested can't stay here.

00:15:17.480 --> 00:15:18.999
I've requested backup...

00:15:19.000 --> 00:15:20.000
from the West District Police Station...

00:15:20.120 --> 00:15:21.600
to take in the suspects over here.

00:15:21.760 --> 00:15:23.200
The higher-ups have also approved it.

00:15:23.520 --> 00:15:25.440
He said if there are too many of them,

00:15:25.600 --> 00:15:26.640
they can be transferred to the prison...

00:15:26.880 --> 00:15:28.360
for temporary detention.

00:15:33.840 --> 00:15:35.200
This is a tough battle.

00:15:36.480 --> 00:15:37.480
We can't let them succeed.

00:16:04.560 --> 00:16:05.560
Boss.

00:16:12.440 --> 00:16:13.480
It's quite bouncy.

00:16:16.680 --> 00:16:17.680
Be careful.

00:16:18.720 --> 00:16:19.920
You're faster than me.

00:16:20.040 --> 00:16:22.000
- Alright. - Go back.

00:16:22.200 --> 00:16:23.400
Be careful.

00:16:23.840 --> 00:16:25.160
- Slowly. - Be careful.

00:16:28.440 --> 00:16:29.440
Take your medicine.

00:16:41.640 --> 00:16:43.480
I'll give you half an hour to take a shower.

00:16:49.280 --> 00:16:50.440
- Young Master Gang. - What's wrong with you?

00:16:54.960 --> 00:16:55.960
Young Master Gang, are you all right?

00:16:56.160 --> 00:16:57.160
Go away!

00:16:58.320 --> 00:16:59.320
Back off!

00:17:00.640 --> 00:17:01.640
Go!

00:17:03.320 --> 00:17:05.120
Young Master Gang, this is a hospital.

00:17:06.960 --> 00:17:08.280
Yes, this is a hospital.

00:17:08.360 --> 00:17:09.920
Hey, how about this?

00:17:10.160 --> 00:17:11.280
Arrange a girl for me.

00:17:11.440 --> 00:17:12.720
She can pretend to be a nurse.

00:17:18.880 --> 00:17:19.880
Young Master Lie wanted to see me.

00:17:20.400 --> 00:17:22.280
Hey, take care of Xiao Lie.

00:17:24.360 --> 00:17:26.120
It's okay. Take them away.

00:17:26.520 --> 00:17:28.520
Just leave. Stop dawdling.

00:17:30.160 --> 00:17:31.160
Hey, Luo Qiang.

00:17:31.400 --> 00:17:32.520
I want two girls.

00:18:52.200 --> 00:18:53.200
Yi Wei.

00:18:54.080 --> 00:18:55.080
You're my son.

00:18:55.840 --> 00:18:56.920
I won't abandon you.

00:18:57.280 --> 00:18:58.960
No matter what happens.

00:18:59.880 --> 00:19:00.880
Understand?

00:19:14.040 --> 00:19:15.040
Let go!

00:19:30.880 --> 00:19:31.880
Congratulations.

00:19:31.920 --> 00:19:34.080
This move is your way to lure the snake out, isn't it?

00:19:34.880 --> 00:19:35.880
Wait.

00:19:38.520 --> 00:19:40.280
Come on, share it with me.

00:19:43.680 --> 00:19:44.680
It's simple.

00:19:45.240 --> 00:19:47.200
Since they can't send outsiders in,

00:19:47.320 --> 00:19:48.320
they can only use...

00:19:48.321 --> 00:19:50.160
someone already locked up in here to do the job.

00:19:50.840 --> 00:19:51.840
I've checked.

00:19:52.040 --> 00:19:53.599
There were two detainees already held here...

00:19:53.600 --> 00:19:55.040
awaiting court appearances.

00:19:55.200 --> 00:19:56.200
It's most likely them.

00:19:56.600 --> 00:19:58.240
Because they're both Han Kui Long's men.

00:19:58.960 --> 00:20:00.319
And among these two,

00:20:00.320 --> 00:20:02.519
one of them made a phone call...

00:20:02.520 --> 00:20:03.520
after Qin Yi Wei went inside,

00:20:03.880 --> 00:20:06.200
then told our staff that he had a stomachache,

00:20:06.280 --> 00:20:07.280
and had to go to the bathroom.

00:20:08.120 --> 00:20:09.200
I just went with the flow,

00:20:09.520 --> 00:20:10.520
and let him go to the bathroom.

00:20:10.840 --> 00:20:13.159
That means you let Qin Yi Wei go in,

00:20:13.160 --> 00:20:14.160
then forced him to make a move.

00:20:14.560 --> 00:20:15.560
That's right.

00:20:15.600 --> 00:20:16.600
Amazing.

00:20:16.800 --> 00:20:19.359
Until Qin Yi Wei is safely brought to court,

00:20:19.360 --> 00:20:20.839
our mission remains unfinished.

00:20:20.840 --> 00:20:22.360
That's why I would say...

00:20:23.200 --> 00:20:25.240
it still depends on your hard work going forward.

00:20:26.880 --> 00:20:28.160
I'll get back to work, Officer Hu.

00:20:29.520 --> 00:20:30.520
Wait a minute.

00:20:30.640 --> 00:20:33.120
One last question. I really have a doubt I'd like to ask you.

00:20:33.560 --> 00:20:35.439
Was that criminal really having stomach pain,

00:20:35.440 --> 00:20:36.480
or was he faking it?

00:20:37.800 --> 00:20:39.040
Go to the toilet and see for yourself.

00:20:53.040 --> 00:20:54.040
Young Master Lie.

00:20:55.000 --> 00:20:57.039
The settlement money for the fellows arrested today...

00:20:57.040 --> 00:20:58.040
has already been distributed.

00:20:58.560 --> 00:20:59.600
What about Li's share?

00:21:00.160 --> 00:21:02.039
He was sentenced to life for murder.

00:21:02.040 --> 00:21:03.040
Besides the money,

00:21:03.240 --> 00:21:04.960
we also gave his family a house.

00:21:06.520 --> 00:21:09.080
It's worth it for Qin Yi Wei's life.

00:21:14.200 --> 00:21:15.200
