00:36:39.080 --> 00:36:41.080
Councilor Huang has another appointment.

00:36:41.480 --> 00:36:43.159
If you have any questions,

00:36:43.160 --> 00:36:44.200
feel free to contact me.

00:36:44.880 --> 00:36:45.880
This is my business card.

00:37:04.280 --> 00:37:05.280
Boss.

00:37:57.240 --> 00:37:58.880
Do we really need a priest at the church?

00:37:59.120 --> 00:38:00.279
I heard from Mr. Qiang...

00:38:00.280 --> 00:38:01.400
that Young Master Gang was severely injured,

00:38:01.720 --> 00:38:02.760
and almost died.

00:38:03.280 --> 00:38:05.280
Luckily, we got a priest to perform an exorcism on him.

00:38:05.680 --> 00:38:07.439
He even said that his epilepsy...

00:38:07.440 --> 00:38:08.440
was caused by a ghost possessing him.

00:38:08.560 --> 00:38:10.279
So he wants to get a priest...

00:38:10.280 --> 00:38:11.520
to perform an exorcism on him.

00:38:12.080 --> 00:38:14.399
On one hand, he wants a priest to perform an exorcism on him.

00:38:14.400 --> 00:38:16.200
On the other, he needs a girl to vent his frustrations.

00:38:16.720 --> 00:38:18.000
Luckily, I'm smart.

00:38:18.280 --> 00:38:20.000
I got the priest to come over...

00:38:20.280 --> 00:38:21.880
for an exorcism at 1pm on Friday.

00:38:22.200 --> 00:38:23.439
I've also arranged for a massage girl...

00:38:23.440 --> 00:38:25.240
to come at a different time.

00:38:36.160 --> 00:38:37.160
Here.

00:38:37.161 --> 00:38:38.200
Be careful, it's hot.

00:38:38.760 --> 00:38:39.840
Sit down and drink slowly.

00:38:42.720 --> 00:38:43.720
Mr. Fei.

00:38:44.560 --> 00:38:45.640
Your business is doing well.

00:38:46.320 --> 00:38:48.000
Thanks to my regulars.

00:38:48.920 --> 00:38:49.920
Just like you.

00:38:50.280 --> 00:38:51.760
Every day at 1:15pm,

00:38:52.000 --> 00:38:53.599
just thinking about Judge Qin,

00:38:53.600 --> 00:38:55.120
here you are!

00:38:55.880 --> 00:38:57.200
I wouldn't have noticed if you hadn't said that.

00:38:57.560 --> 00:38:59.800
I feel off without your coffee every day.

00:39:00.280 --> 00:39:01.319
Give me a minute.

00:39:01.320 --> 00:39:02.800
- I'll make yours right away. - Okay.

00:39:15.920 --> 00:39:19.400
(Hokong Maximum Security Prison)

00:39:19.520 --> 00:39:20.560
I'm sorry.

00:39:21.200 --> 00:39:23.600
Li messed up.

00:39:26.520 --> 00:39:27.800
There's still a whole year.

00:39:28.760 --> 00:39:30.440
There's still time. There's no need to rush.

00:39:31.760 --> 00:39:33.119
It's all that Councilor's fault.

00:39:33.120 --> 00:39:34.480
He went to inspect the prison.

00:39:34.840 --> 00:39:36.280
The prison is under tight surveillance now.

00:39:37.160 --> 00:39:39.240
I said there's time. No need to rush.

00:39:41.600 --> 00:39:42.600
Luo Qiang...

00:39:43.520 --> 00:39:45.880
said your brother wants to hire a priest.

00:39:47.240 --> 00:39:48.280
My brother said...

00:39:48.680 --> 00:39:50.400
he believed epilepsy was caused by ghost possession.

00:39:50.840 --> 00:39:52.040
He won't take medicine.

00:39:52.200 --> 00:39:54.000
So he needs a priest to help him perform an exorcism.

00:39:55.040 --> 00:39:56.800
He's out of his mind.

00:39:57.880 --> 00:39:58.880
I don't think so.

00:39:59.560 --> 00:40:00.839
Besides the priest,

00:40:00.840 --> 00:40:02.040
he's also looking for girls.

00:40:03.720 --> 00:40:05.000
He's perfectly normal.

00:40:17.680 --> 00:40:18.680
Xiao Lie.

00:40:19.600 --> 00:40:21.840
You and your brother are very close.

00:40:22.440 --> 00:40:23.880
Future matters at home...

00:40:24.920 --> 00:40:26.360
are now in the hands of you two brothers.

00:40:27.520 --> 00:40:29.440
You didn't like to get involved before.

00:40:29.920 --> 00:40:32.160
That's why I kept a lot of things from you.

00:40:33.000 --> 00:40:34.000
You didn't know.

00:40:34.280 --> 00:40:37.520
That's why you couldn't guess what my decision would be.

00:40:40.880 --> 00:40:42.199
Twenty years ago,

00:40:42.200 --> 00:40:43.480
how did I...

00:40:43.720 --> 00:40:45.240
rise to the top so quickly?

00:40:46.400 --> 00:40:48.519
Because I was targeted...

00:40:48.520 --> 00:40:50.920
by a very powerful interest group.

00:40:51.840 --> 00:40:52.880
How powerful is it?

00:40:54.320 --> 00:40:55.320
In politics and business?

00:41:02.000 --> 00:41:03.080
In the police force and among gangsters.

00:41:04.840 --> 00:41:05.880
All of them.

00:41:06.880 --> 00:41:08.560
They never show their faces.

00:41:09.560 --> 00:41:12.160
They just send messages through middlemen.

00:41:12.760 --> 00:41:14.000
I worked for them.

00:41:14.960 --> 00:41:16.200
They supported me,

00:41:16.880 --> 00:41:18.080
and I could...

00:41:18.680 --> 00:41:21.560
grow step by step.

00:41:23.080 --> 00:41:24.560
If they're so powerful,

00:41:25.080 --> 00:41:26.400
why did you end up in prison?

00:41:27.360 --> 00:41:29.040
I was too arrogant.

00:41:29.600 --> 00:41:31.400
They used the assault case...

00:41:32.800 --> 00:41:33.960
to teach me a lesson.

00:41:35.440 --> 00:41:36.840
They've already agreed...

00:41:37.760 --> 00:41:39.480
on my future benefits.

00:41:41.000 --> 00:41:42.000
Is it worth it?

00:41:42.160 --> 00:41:43.200
Yes.

00:41:43.520 --> 00:41:45.800
I can help both of you brothers to the top.

00:41:46.240 --> 00:41:49.480
I can also make our Han Group...

00:41:49.720 --> 00:41:53.960
the largest gambling empire in Hokong.

00:41:54.840 --> 00:41:56.000
It's worth it.

00:41:57.800 --> 00:42:00.000
I'm almost there.

00:42:00.680 --> 00:42:02.400
The land acquisition plan of the Old City District...

00:42:02.680 --> 00:42:04.040
will begin soon.

00:42:04.960 --> 00:42:06.800
Let's not do anything unnecessary.

00:42:07.120 --> 00:42:08.520
We have to preserve our strength.

00:42:10.200 --> 00:42:11.560
People who only talk about profit...

00:42:12.200 --> 00:42:13.600
don't care about morals.

00:42:13.800 --> 00:42:15.280
We're in the open while they're in the dark.

00:42:15.760 --> 00:42:17.200
Aren't we at a disadvantage?

00:42:18.760 --> 00:42:20.960
Their identities are top secret.

00:42:21.200 --> 00:42:22.640
Ordinary people can't see them.

00:42:24.000 --> 00:42:25.480
There are certain symbols...

00:42:27.120 --> 00:42:28.960
you should be wary of the moment you see them.

00:42:33.920 --> 00:42:34.960
Plum blossoms...

00:42:36.040 --> 00:42:37.120
represents us,

00:42:37.560 --> 00:42:38.560
the gangsters.

00:42:41.280 --> 00:42:42.320
Diamonds.

00:42:43.120 --> 00:42:44.120
Hearts.

00:42:46.080 --> 00:42:47.120
Spades.

00:42:48.120 --> 00:42:49.120
Business,

00:42:49.360 --> 00:42:50.360
police,

00:42:50.680 --> 00:42:51.680
and politics.

00:42:52.600 --> 00:42:53.640
When you see these,

00:42:54.080 --> 00:42:55.160
you have to be careful.

00:42:55.800 --> 00:42:56.800
You have to be wary.

00:42:57.360 --> 00:42:58.760
You can't touch these people.

00:42:59.600 --> 00:43:00.760
You can't offend them.

00:43:01.880 --> 00:43:03.360
They only care about profit.

00:43:07.800 --> 00:43:08.800
Profit...

00:43:09.200 --> 00:43:11.079
is your greatest weapon.

00:43:11.080 --> 00:43:12.120
Do you understand?

00:43:47.280 --> 00:43:48.320
Son,

00:43:49.720 --> 00:43:51.040
Go check on your little sister, okay?

00:43:51.560 --> 00:43:52.560
Good boy.

00:43:58.520 --> 00:44:00.480
See if you need anything else.

00:44:01.520 --> 00:44:03.000
We can hold out for a while.

00:44:03.960 --> 00:44:05.680
I can't keep going on like this with the kids.

00:44:08.280 --> 00:44:09.680
Any news from the Old City District?

00:44:09.880 --> 00:44:11.759
My dad secretly told me...

00:44:11.760 --> 00:44:13.199
that Qi Chang Rong's men...

00:44:13.200 --> 00:44:14.480
suddenly behaved themselves.

00:44:14.920 --> 00:44:15.999
They didn't commit murder or arson.

00:44:16.000 --> 00:44:17.120
They didn't fight or cause trouble.

00:44:17.960 --> 00:44:19.320
But they sent someone to my house.

00:44:20.360 --> 00:44:22.320
I think they suspect me.

00:44:23.720 --> 00:44:26.080
Because you were the last person to see Qi Chang Rong.

00:44:26.840 --> 00:44:27.920
They'll never guess...

00:44:28.160 --> 00:44:29.200
that you would stay here.

00:44:30.400 --> 00:44:32.479
If Qi Chang Rong's body is found,

00:44:32.480 --> 00:44:34.280
it won't just be the Old City Gang.

00:44:34.720 --> 00:44:35.999
The police won't let me go either.

00:44:36.000 --> 00:44:37.680
That's why I need to get out of here as soon as possible.

00:44:39.440 --> 00:44:40.560
I'll arrange for you to leave.

00:44:41.520 --> 00:44:42.720
Can you leave after Friday?

00:44:42.920 --> 00:44:43.920
Why?

00:44:44.760 --> 00:44:46.960
What could be more important than this right now?

00:44:49.360 --> 00:44:51.000
Because someone is going to die that day.

00:44:58.080 --> 00:44:59.080
I'll see you off.

00:45:00.400 --> 00:45:01.440
I promised Wei.

00:45:24.160 --> 00:45:25.160
Judge Qin.

00:45:36.680 --> 00:45:37.880
I bought it for the kids.

00:45:42.720 --> 00:45:44.000
Be careful.

00:45:45.760 --> 00:45:47.040
Come back safely.

00:45:47.840 --> 00:45:48.880
Okay.